EU

If country = EU:

Include CO₂ emissions per installation.

Include number of EU Allowances (EUAs) purchased/surrendered.

Include detailed fuel and engine data for verification.

If plant < 20 MW → generate optional voluntary carbon neutrality report.

China

If country = China:

Include CO₂ emissions per MWh (intensity).

Check if plant meets efficiency benchmarks; if not, calculate extra allowances required.

Optionally include CCER offsets (up to 5%).

Include verification info from provincial authorities.

US

If country = US:

Include CO₂ emissions per plant.

Include power generation output.

If plant is in a cap-and-trade state → include carbon credits purchased/surrendered.

If outside regulated states → include optional voluntary ESG/credits reporting.
